Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.09,0:00:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Professor Agasa was treating, we went out for sushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we ended up at a revolving sushi shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:11.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first, Genta and the others were disappointed...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they soon understood the charm of revolving sushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And began enjoying their favorite dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:21.49,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,However, a customer next to us named Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:21.49,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\be5}Agatsuma Ryuuzou (43)\NCustomer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Started saying mean things to us and the other customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.66,0:00:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the manager was harassed in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We felt uncomfortable, and decided to leave, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.46,0:00:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} suddenly yelled and collapsed to the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was the scent of bitter almond emanating from his mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:40.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Murder by poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three people had history with him and were natural suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who'd had a dispute with Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nin this very shop - Aizono Osamu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:56.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The woman who had to close her sushi shop due to the review\Nfrom food critic Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} - Takemura Sakiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:01:04.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The manager who was caught in Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s fight and\Ninjured his wrist - the former chef, Namiki Danji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, after the body search, none of those\Nthree were discovered to be carrying poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did the poison go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how did the culprit only target\NAgatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with the poisoned plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is magic, attack the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.26,0:01:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On Saturday nights, be sure to click on Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.68,0:01:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A case at a revolving sushi restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's showtime for the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:33.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, can it be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there a way to make only Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} take the poisoned plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, the menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You would definitely take down something you've ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Order?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:39.91,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:45.28,CharCard - 2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\be5\fad(250,250)}Namiki Danji (39)\NManager
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:42.36,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Once you've selected something from the touch-screen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:45.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The order will be placed on a bowl labeled\N"reserved" and then put onto the belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:48.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,When it reaches your seat, a beep sounds as a reminder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:53.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the one sitting to the right of the victim, Takemura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:56.35,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:00.09,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Even if his order did come around...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:01.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I still wouldn't have been able to poison it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:04:00.55,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\be5\fad(250,250)}Takemura Sakiko (51)\NCustomer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy wearing the hat was sitting next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know which of them ordered it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I couldn't see their touch-screen from my seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I couldn't know what it was they ordered anyway, now could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the one who could see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would be the one sitting next to him, Aizono{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:28.41,CharCard - 3,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\be5\fad(250,250)}Aizono Osamu (32)\NCustomer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.17,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Please, just hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:25.76,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Didn't I say it earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:28.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I was sitting to his left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:31.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The sushi comes around from the right, doesn't is?p
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I had seen what Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} ordered on the touch-screen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't he have taken it before it reached me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not the only one who could see the touch-screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:47.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The manager could, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From after my argument with Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} until he collapsed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The manager was standing right over our shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he was causing such a disturbance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:04.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said his meal would come free of\Ncharge and asked him nicely to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he'd eat more if it was free, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To ensure he didn't cause anymore\Ntrouble, I stood watch behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, while I was watching, he didn't order anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can confirm that with the restaurant computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite already being put through a body search...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And with you finding no poison container...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or even a handkerchief with poison on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still continue to suspect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit must have already escaped with the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you couldn't find any containers housing poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless we locate the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to determine how Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've checked out the computer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there was no order from Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Left?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Left...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man that was killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he was left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because on the tips of his left hand's fingers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were two or three grains of rice stuck to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I saw him eating with his left hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:29.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was picking up his sushi with his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:32.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:35.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was left-handed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you put poison on the left side of most of the plates...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:43.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be possible to make him touch it that way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:46.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check all plates on the belt and see if\Nthere's any poison on them as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forensics, if you would...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that deduction correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit probably made sure that only Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was\Nleft handed among us before applying the poison, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if another left-handed customer came in later?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Left-handed or not, most kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still pick up plates with both hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, where did the poison go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without a container or cloth-like\Nmaterial, it would be difficult to poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something next to Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The corner of a plastic packet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:08:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though there were many plates on the belt\Nwhen Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} took the poisoned plate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were any of the other plates poisoned?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not a single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, it's as if the victim were hypnotized...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To take only the plate laced with poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe there was a message card on the plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:22.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like, "This is a present for you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't take a plate like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sounds eerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there wasn't any card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there had been one, the victim would still have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care about any of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:43.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we just ate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of that sushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I eat all of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it'll just be thrown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a waste?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:00.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it was done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you lend me a handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to wipe my glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, use one of the restaurant's hand wipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're by the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a trick that can only be accomplished with sushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, the culprit is that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be able to poison only Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, while\Nusing this trick to dispose of the evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A clever trick centered around this revolving sushi's special system.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Officers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you still suspecting us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's understandable for you to suspect us due\Nto our conflicts with Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the only plate that was poisoned\Nwas the one Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} took...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it would've been impossible\Nfor us to have predicted that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You three did have a chance to poison the plate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, how about you please try to explain it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did we force that man to take\Nthe only plate laced with poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do any of us look like the type of cold-\Nblooded killer who would kill at random?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:26.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if we wanted to apply poison, we\Ndon't have any container for that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If one of us were the culprit, something\Nlike that would still be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Considering from the time when that man\Ncollapsed to when you got here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:43.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of us moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:50.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit must've been one of the customers who already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That also explains why no containers housing poison were found.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:57.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who is long gone left the poisoned plate with\Nthe intention of committing a random murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} just had the unfortunate luck of taking that plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It certainly was bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:12.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using my voice without warning again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm not talking about the murdered Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean the snickering culprit who thought they had succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because not only the method by which\NAgatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But also the trick used to get rid of the poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will soon be exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:34.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By me, who came here by chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And my humble deduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it's true? The culprit is among them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, just as you police suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who had a grudge against Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of those three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying things like that out of the blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:08.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just because you're a little large doesn't mean\Nyou can bluff like you're some great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Size doesn't matter, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of us put poison on that plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:24.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the one who did it was Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor, please act more like a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the one who put poison on the plate was the victim himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't this be a suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, what I mean is that the poison wasn't only on the plate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But also on something he touched before he took the plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was why only Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s plate had poison on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.32,0:12:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what's that "something"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:12:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When your favorite sushi comes around in a revolving sushi shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you pick up before taking the plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pick up my chopsticks first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pick up my cup to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:14.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pick up the soy sauce bottle and pour some.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I don't mean before taking your first plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But instead what you pick up each time you finish any plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta would definitely do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of the things at Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s seat were\Ntested, and none of them had poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So no matter what he picked up before taking the plate...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what's at Mitsuhiko's seat, but not Genta's?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not listening...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, chopsticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s seat doesn't have chopsticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} used his hands to eat, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My Dad told me before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're from Tokyo, you gotta eat sushi with your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:59.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, after using your hands, there's\Nsomething you'd want to pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something I'd pick up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd pick up my fingers and lick them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after licking your fingers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hand wipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you're directly touching the sushi\Nrice and toppings with your fingers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before taking the next plate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd want to wipe off the oil, water,\Nand sticky rice with the hand wipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:27.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the poison was placed in the hand wipe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the case, right, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there wasn't a hand wipe at Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you can see some traces of it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's from what you can pick up for\Nfree at the entrance of the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Traces of the plastic packet for a disposable hand wipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:58.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit likely put the poison into the\Npacket of the hand wipe beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using something like a syringe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking a plate after wiping your\Nhand with the poisoned hand wipe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:10.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then using those same fingers\Nto eat sushi would result in death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, only your plate would have poison on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was poisoned, he ate a lot of sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:26.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he come across the poisoned hand wipe earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was switched out at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Possibly when he was arguing with the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If someone happened to touch your hand wipe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:43.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And say, "What are you doing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if we suppose the culprit knew Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nwould put the hand wipe down next to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But people can vary on where they put something down...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:16:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time he used the hand wipe after eating,\Nhe'd naturally put it down on his left side, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, the one sitting to the left of Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aizono{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hand wipe was placed right next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sitting to the left of Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you pretend the poisoned wipe\Nis your own and put it next to his...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:22.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Switching them would be no trouble at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That poisoned hand wipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was I carrying anything like that, Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We conducted a body search, but didn't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you insist on naming me as the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then first explain how the poisoned\Nhand wipe disappeared on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:47.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It didn't disappear on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You made it happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By using something that automatically removes\Nplates after a certain amount of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This revolving sushi's transport system!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:17:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The revolving sushi here automatically removes\Ndishes that have been on the belt for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used this system for his trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He likely did it when Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was poisoned and collapsed;\Nwhile everyone was focusing their attention on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he wrapped Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s hand wipe around the packet\Nand poisoned wipe, and then put them on a plate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.88,0:17:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one around them would notice because\Nboth the hand wipe and rice are white.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While it's true that the hand wipes could be\Ndisposed of by the belt, would it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Putting a plate back on the belt is bad manners, and\Nsomeone would've noticed something this outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.73,0:17:41.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whether they noticed or not, everyone was doing the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:43.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were saying, "It's food poisoning!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Don't eat that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Put your plate back."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since everyone was doing it, no one cared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wasn't the conveyor belt stopped immediately?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:17:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I stopped it about two or three\Nminutes after Agatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be strange for the machine\Nto dispose of it in such a short time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that if it were a plate that had just been\Nremoved, it would take a while to be recycled, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it had been switched with the first plate you had taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The machine would scan the microcode and\Nthink it had been on the belt for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it'd be recycled immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is the disposed sushi placed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's in the kitchen waste bin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:38.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, check that waste bin now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The poisoned hand wipe and packet must be in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aizono{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:49.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If your fingerprints are found on the packet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That will be conclusive evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you are our culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:19:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your motive would be the argument you had with\NAgatsuma{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in this shop previously, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall, that was about you being corrected after\Nconfusing sea bass with flounder in front of your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I had a cold at the time, so my taste was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's not the reason I had gotten it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sea bass had been switched onto the more\Nexpensive flounder plate, that was why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Switched?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was that Agatsuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He saw me showing off in front of my wife and wanted to bully me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he switched the flounder and sea bass on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, he visited my food blog and\Nwrote demeaning comments on it everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though my wife told me to pay him no mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bastard with a rotten heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said whatever he wanted about\Nfood just because he's a food critic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's the reason you poisoned him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:03.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since then, nothing I've eaten has tasted good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:10.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, my wife ended up divorcing me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only loved to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only wanted to see my wife's happy face while\Neating food from restaurants I recommended...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But mister, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who stained what you loved...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was you, yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stain that can never be wiped away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The poison known as "murder."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, the packet and poisoned hand wipe were\Nfound in the waste bin, and the case was closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.31,0:21:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sushi that had stopped has likely begun revolving again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:04.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't think I'll have any for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, revolving sushi only reminds me of this annoying case...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.48,0:22:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, even though I won't be having any revolving sushi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.44,0:22:32.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.45,0:22:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This restaurant is good, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.53,0:22:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's addictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two eel plates for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:42.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sushi has always been a proud part of\NJapanese culinary culture around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.37,0:22:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder we Japanese enjoy eating it so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.92,0:22:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, there's a new one in front of the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.13,0:22:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A revolving sushi shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.18,0:22:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:58.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, let's have the Professor take us there next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:22:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.52,0:23:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That will be 12,500 yen, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you make some sort of mistake, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.82,0:23:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fruit parfait was tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:19.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So was Ayumi's pudding Ã  la mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had all of the desserts, and they were great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did we have parfait and pudding, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.33,0:23:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.37,0:23:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're slightly more expensive than the sushi is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.21,0:23:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't we make every Saturday Sushi Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi agrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:42.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.43,0:23:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Boys - Saturday is for revolving sushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.77,0:23:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My eyes are revolving, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.48,0:23:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because you were stingy in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.53,0:23:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Nationwide Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} Competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, Genta's dad is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.66,0:24:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of our suspects?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.64,0:24:28.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.06,0:24:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.11,0:24:33.22,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, Genta's dad will makes his debut!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.22,0:24:34.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Not the culprit, not the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.89,0:24:36.01,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,OK, cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.11,0:24:36.45,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode
